#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Tails report for October, 2013\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"گزارش اکتبر ۲۰۱۳ تیلز\"]]\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Releases\n"
msgstr "انتشارها\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Tails 0.21 [[was released|news/version_0.21]] on October 29."
msgstr "تیلز ۰٫۲۱ روز ۲۹ اکتبر [[منتشر شد|news/version_0.21]]."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails 0.22 is "
"[scheduled](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2013-September/003718.html)  "
"for December 11."
msgstr ""
"تیلز ۰٫۲۲ [قرار است](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-"
"dev/2013-September/003718.html) ۱۱ دسامبر منتشر شود."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Metrics\n"
msgstr "متریک‌ها\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Tails has been started more than 189 979 times in October.  This makes a "
"boot every 14 seconds on average."
msgstr ""
"تیلز بیش از ۱۸۹٫۹۷۹ بار در ماه اکتبر راه‌اندازی شد. یعنی به طور متوسط هر ۱۴ "
"ثانیه یک راه‌اندازی."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "15 226 downloads of the OpenPGP signature of Tails ISO."
msgstr "- ۱۵٫۲۲۷ دانلود امضای اُپن‌پی‌جی‌پی ایزوی تیلز."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "86 reports were received through WhisperBack."
msgstr "۸۶ گزارش از طریق ویسپربک دریافت شدند."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Code\n"
msgstr "کد\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Andres Gomez Ramirez proposed an [initial "
"patch](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2013-October/003810.html)  "
"to warn when caps-lock in on in the Greeter ([[!tails_ticket 5917]])."
msgstr ""
"آندرس گومز رامیرز [بسته‌ای مقدماتی](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-"
"dev/2013-October/003810.html) برای هشدار روشن بودن کلید قفل تبدیل در "
"خوشامدگو پیشنهاد کرد ([[!tails_ticket 5917]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We had a low-hanging fruits session [on October "
"12](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2013-October/003860.html), "
"and malaparte couldn't stop in the end :)"
msgstr ""
"یک جلسه برای انجام کارهای آسان دردسترس در [۱۲ "
"اکتبر](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2013-October/003860.html)"
" داشتیم و malaparte در پایان جلسه بی‌خیال کار نمی‌شد :)"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some issues were fixed for the migration to [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"feature/wheezy desc=\"Tails Wheezy\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 6015]])."
msgstr ""
"مشکلاتی در رابطه با کوچ به [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/wheezy desc=\""
"Tails Wheezy\"]] حل شدند ([[!tails_ticket 6015]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The branch for SD cards support wired via [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"feature/sdio desc=\"SDIO\"]] was merged ([[!tails_ticket 6324]])."
msgstr ""
"شاخهٔ پشتیبانی از کارت‌های حافظه [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/sdio desc=\""
"SDIO\"]] ادغام شد ([[!tails_ticket 6324]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/vagrant-libvirt desc=\"initial work\"]] "
"to build Tails with vagrant-libvirt was done "
"([[blueprint|blueprint/vagrant-libvirt]], [[!tails_ticket 6212]])."
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/vagrant-libvirt desc=\"کارهایی مقدماتی\"]] "
"برای ساخت تیلز با vagrant-libvirt انجام شدند ([[blueprint|blueprint/vagrant-"
"libvirt]]،  [[!tails_ticket 6212]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"A [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/stronger-gnupg-cipher desc=\"branch\"]] to "
"use stronger ciphers in GnuPG was prepared and merged."
msgstr ""
"یک [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/stronger-gnupg-cipher desc=\"شاخه\"]] برای "
"استفاده از سایفرهای قوی‌تر در GnuPG آماده و ادغام شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Kevin C. Krinke is [working on](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/kevin/clock/) a "
"clock applet that allows displays local time, while keeping UTC as the "
"system timezone."
msgstr ""
"Kevin C. Krinke [در حال کار روی](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/kevin/clock/) "
"یک برنامک ساعت است که ساعت محلی را نیز نشان می‌دهد و در عین حال ساعت گرینویچ "
"را ساعت سیستم نگاه می‌دارد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "[[!tails_gitweb_branch test/fix-detection-of-used-display]] was merged."
msgstr "[[!tails_gitweb_branch test/fix-detection-of-used-display]] ادغام شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/Debian-proposed-updates]] was merged, and "
"reverted after the Squeeze point-release was out."
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/Debian-proposed-updates]] پس از انتشار نسخهٔ "
"جزیی Squeeze ادغام و بازگشت داده شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Tails now uses the [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"feature/same-startpage-custom-url-as-tbb desc=\"same custom Startpage URL as "
"the TBB\"]]."
msgstr ""
"تیلز حالا از [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/same-startpage-custom-url-as-tbb "
"desc=\"نشانی صفحهٔ آغاز یکسان با TBB\"]] استفاده می‌کند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The ikiwiki setup was [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/simplify_ikiwiki_setup "
"desc=\"simplified\"]]."
msgstr ""
"تظنیمات ikiwiki [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/simplify_ikiwiki_setup desc=\""
"ساده‌سازی شدند\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/persistent_printers desc=\"fixes\"]] to "
"the persistent printers feature were prepared and merged."
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/persistent_printers desc=\"بهبودهایی\"]] در "
"ویژگی درایو مانا آماده و ادغام شدند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"A web browser resizing bug was [partially "
"fixed](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/torbutton/tag/?id=debian/1.5.2-2)  "
"([[!tails_ticket 6377]])."
msgstr ""
"یک ایراد تغییر اندازهٔ مرورگر وب [تا حدودی برطرف شد](https://git-"
"tails.immerda.ch/torbutton/tag/?id=debian/1.5.2-2)  ([[!tails_ticket 6377]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Now installing Linux 3.10.x [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/linux-3.10.11 "
"desc=\"from Debian testing\"]]."
msgstr ""
"حالا لینوکس ۳٫۱۰٫x را [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/linux-3.10.11 desc=\""
"دبیان آزمایشی نصب می‌کنیم\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The [[!tails_gitweb_branch security/vidalia_in_its_own_user "
"desc=\"branch\"]] to run Vidalia as its own user was polished and "
"merged. Too bad nobody detected at RC stage the regression it brought, that "
"made its way into Tails 0.21. Did we mention you should test our release "
"candidates?"
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch security/vidalia_in_its_own_user desc=\"branch\"]] "
"برای اجرای ویدالیا به عنوان کاربر خود بهبود یافته و ادغام شد. متأسفانه کسی "
"متوجه رگرسیونی که در مرحلهٔ آرسی از آن ناشی می‌شد نشد و این مشکل در تیلز ۰٫"
"۲۱ ادامه پیدا کرد. قبلاً گفته‌ایم که خوب است نامزدهای انتشار ما را آزمایش "
"کنید؟"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The branch [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/consistent-peristence-path "
"desc=\"branch\"]] to have a consistent path to the persistent volume "
"mountpoint was polished and merged ([[!tails_ticket 5854]])."
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/consistent-peristence-path desc=\"شاخه‌ای\"]] "
"برای داشتن مسیری سازگار به نقطهٔ اتصال درایو مانا بهبود یافته و ادغام شد ([["
"!tails_ticket 5854]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The work towards MAC spoofing [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/spoof-mac "
"desc=\"went on\"]]."
msgstr ""
"کارها برای جازنی آدرس مک [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/spoof-mac desc=\""
"ادامه یافت\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Various regressions detected in 0.21~rc1 were fixed in time for the 0.21 "
"final release. Not all, unfortunately."
msgstr ""
"رگرسیون‌های متعددی که در 0.21~rc1 یافت شده بودند به‌موقع برای نسخهٔ نهایی ۰٫"
"۲۱ برطرف شدند، البته متأسفانه نه همهٔ آن‌ها."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/ff24 desc=\"initial work\"]] was done "
"towards the migration to Torbutton 1.6.x ([[!tails_ticket 6371]]) and "
"Firefox 24 ([[!tails_ticket 6370]])."
msgstr ""
"برخی [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/ff24 desc=\"کارهای مقدماتی\"]] برای کوچ "
"به تورباتن ۱٫۶٫x ([[!tails_ticket 6371]]) و فایرفاکس ۲۴ ([[!tails_ticket "
"6370]]) انجام شدند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"A [[!debbug 725779 desc=\"plan\"]] was proposed to fix OTR protocol "
"downgrade in Debian Squeeze and Wheezy."
msgstr ""
"[[!debbug 725779 desc=\"طرحی\"]] برای رفع مشکل ارتقاء به عقب پروتکل OTR در "
"دبیان‌های Squeeze و Wheezy مطرح شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some build-dependencies for Tails software were uploaded to Debian, and "
"accepted: [[!debpts libdist-zilla-plugin-test-notabs-perl]], [[!debpts "
"libdist-zilla-plugin-test-perl-critic-perl]] and [[!debpts "
"libdist-zilla-plugin-installguide-perl]]."
msgstr ""
"بعضی وابستگی‌های ساخت نرم‌افزار تیلز روی دبیان آپلود شده و پذیرفته شدند: [["
"!debpts libdist-zilla-plugin-test-notabs-perl]]، [[!debpts libdist-zilla-"
"plugin-test-perl-critic-perl]] و [[!debpts libdist-zilla-plugin-installguide-"
"perl]]."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "An initscript for Tahoe-LAFS has been [[!debbug 652003 desc=\"written\"]]."
msgstr ""
"یک initscript  برای Tahoe-LAFS [[!debbug 652003 desc=\"نوشته شده‌است\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "killyourtv volunteered to maintain I2P in Tails."
msgstr "killyourtv  داوطلب نگهداری I2P در تیلز شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "Incremental updates were worked on."
msgstr "روی ارتقاهای تدریجی کار شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"[[!debpts bilibop]] 0.4.17, 0.4.17~bpo70+1, 0.4.18 and 0.4.19 were uploaded "
"to Debian."
msgstr ""
"[[!debpts bilibop]] 0.4.17، 0.4.17~bpo70+1، 0.4.18 و 0.4.19 روی دبیان آپلود "
"شدند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "[[!debpts mat]] 0.4-1 and 0.4.2-1 were uploaded to Debian."
msgstr "[[!debpts mat]] 0.4-1 و 0.4.2-1 روی دبیان آپلود شدند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "A few patches for AppArmor profiles were submitted upstream."
msgstr "چند بسته برای پروفایل‌های اپ‌آرمور در آپ‌استریم ثبت شدند."

